      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 2018 Lexus RX 350 is a standout example of luxury meeting longevity. Finished in a sophisticated Nebula Gray Pearl, the body retains a deep luster, though it shows minor, expected road wear such as small stone chips on the front bumper. The interior is a sanctuary of Parchment leather that has been kept smoke-free and regularly conditioned; while the driver's seat shows very light bolster creasing, the cabin remains remarkably fresh. All premium features, including the navigation system, heated steering wheel, and power liftgate, are in perfect working order. Under the hood, the V6 engine runs whisper-quiet, backed by a comprehensive dealership service history. The tires have approximately 60% tread remaining, and the brakes were recently serviced. Apart from a few faint scratches near the rear cargo area from routine use, this vehicle is aesthetically pleasing and mechanically robust, offering a smooth, confident ride for its next owner.",
